content:
with pulse pounding beats mind altering synths rapid fire rhythms and mutilated unrecognizable samples Concrete and Steel offers a showcase of the best up and coming underground electronic producers as well as a celebration of the most influential PERIOD A reflection of the cyberpunk dystopia that becomes more real each day but also resilience in the face of it Concrete and Steel brings you an escape from monotony with a curated collection of beats perfect for a gabber apocalypse a techno punk rave or a late night gaming session PERIOD Plug in and turn up with the best in techno breakbeat noise and gabber PERIOD
